📋 Business Report
12-page executive PDF generated with Python ReportLab:
📌 Executive Summary — colour-coded insight boxes, KPI cards
📂 Dataset Overview — schema, column types, YoY patient volume
👥 Patient Demographics — age groups, gender, admission type analysis
🦠 Diagnosis Trends — condition stats, test outcomes, medication usage
💰 Financial Performance — billing analysis, LOS correlation, cost per day
🏦 Insurance Provider Analysis — revenue share, avg claims, volume
💡 8 Key Findings — F1–F8 colour-coded insight cards
✅ 6 Business Recommendations — actionable next steps
📚 Appendix — full data dictionary (26 columns with formulas)
