⚙️ Setup & Installation
Prerequisites
```bash
Python 3.10+
Jupyter Notebook
Power BI Desktop   # for .pbix file
PostgreSQL         # optional — SQLite/DuckDB also works
```
Install Dependencies
```bash
pip install pandas numpy matplotlib seaborn reportlab jupyter
```
Run the Project
```bash
# Step 1: Place dataset
cp healthcare_dataset.csv data/raw/

# Step 2: Run notebooks in order
jupyter notebook notebooks/01_data_cleaning.ipynb
jupyter notebook notebooks/02_eda_demographics.ipynb
jupyter notebook notebooks/03_eda_diagnosis.ipynb
jupyter notebook notebooks/04_eda_financial.ipynb

# Step 3: Load SQL
duckdb < sql/01_schema_setup.sql
duckdb < sql/02_diagnosis_queries.sql

# Step 4: Open Power BI dashboard
# Open dashboard/healthcare_diagnosis_dashboard.pbix in Power BI Desktop

# Step 5: View the report
open reports/Healthcare_Diagnosis_Financial_Report.pdf
```
